Class FullyConnectedReferenceLayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.ReferenceCountingBase

          • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.layers.java.FullyConnectedReferenceLayer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Layer, ReferenceCounting, Serializable

    public class FullyConnectedReferenceLayer
extends LayerBase
    A dense matrix operator using vector-matrix multiplication. Represents a fully connected layer of synapses, where all inputs are connected to all outputs via seperate coefficients.
    See Also:
